Slim black boy Blue Cole has just learned this the hard way and is now stranded in the woods. Fortunately country boy Dustin arrives in his white van and agrees to give him a ride, for a fee. Desperate and broke, Cole reluctantly sexually submits to the bearded brute. Dustin ties him up, slaps him around, brutally pounds his tight ass then hoses him with a big facial cumshot.
title: Blue Cole stranded in the woods
